{"book": 7, "chapter": 5, "sections": [{"type": "heading", "heading": "底波拉和巴拉的歌"}, {"type": "paragraph", "contents": [{"verseNum": 1, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "那時，底波拉和亞比挪菴的兒子巴拉作歌，說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 1, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 2, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "因為以色列中有軍長率領，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 2, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "百姓也甘心犧牲自己，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 2, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "你們應當頌讚耶和華！"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 2, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 3, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "君王啊，要聽！"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 3, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "王子啊，要側耳而聽！"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 3, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "我要向耶和華歌唱；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 3, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "我要歌頌耶和華－以色列的神。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 3, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 4, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "耶和華啊，你從西珥出來，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 4, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "由以東地行走。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 4, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "那時地震天漏，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 4, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "雲也落雨。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 4, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 5, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "山見耶和華的面就震動，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 5, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " 西奈山見耶和華－以色列神的面也是如此。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 5, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 6, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "在亞拿之子珊迦的時候，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 6, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "又在雅億的日子，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 6, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "大道無人行走，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 6, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "都是繞道而行。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 6, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 7, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 以色列中的官長停職，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 7, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "直到我底波拉興起，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 7, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "等我興起作以色列的母。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 7, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 以色列人選擇新神，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "爭戰的事就臨到城門。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "那時，以色列四萬人中"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "豈能見盾牌槍矛呢？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 9, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "我心傾向以色列的首領，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 9, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他們在民中甘心犧牲自己。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 9, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "你們應當頌讚耶和華！"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 9, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "騎白驢的、坐繡花毯子的、行路的，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "你們都當傳揚！"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 11, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "在遠離弓箭響聲打水之處，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 11, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "人必述說耶和華公義的作為，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 11, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "就是他治理以色列公義的作為。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 11, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "那時耶和華的民下到城門。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 11, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 12, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 底波拉啊，興起！興起！"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 12, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "你當興起，興起，唱歌。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 12, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " 亞比挪菴的兒子巴拉啊，你當奮興，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 12, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "擄掠你的敵人。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 12, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 13, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "那時有餘剩的貴冑和百姓一同下來；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 13, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "耶和華降臨，為我攻擊勇士。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 13, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 14, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "有根本在亞瑪力人的地，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 14, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "從以法蓮下來的；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 14, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " 便雅憫在民中跟隨你。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 14, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "有掌權的從瑪吉下來；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 14, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "有持杖檢點民數的從西布倫下來；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 14, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 15, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 以薩迦的首領與底波拉同來；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 15, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " 以薩迦怎樣，巴拉也怎樣。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 15, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "眾人都跟隨巴拉衝下平原；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 15, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "在呂便的溪水旁有心中定大志的。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 15, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "你為何坐在羊圈內"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "聽羣中吹笛的聲音呢？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "在呂便的溪水旁有心中設大謀的。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 17, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 基列人安居在約旦河外。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 17, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " 但人為何等在船上？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 17, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " 亞設人在海口靜坐，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 17, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "在港口安居。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 17, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 18, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 西布倫人是拚命敢死的；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 18, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " 拿弗他利人在田野的高處也是如此。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 18, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 19, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "君王都來爭戰。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 19, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "那時迦南諸王在米吉多水旁的他納爭戰，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 19, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "卻未得擄掠銀錢。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 19, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 20, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "星宿從天上爭戰，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 20, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "從其軌道攻擊西西拉。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 20, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 21, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 基順古河把敵人沖沒；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 21, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "我的靈啊，應當努力前行。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 21, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 22, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "那時壯馬馳驅，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 22, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "踢跳，奔騰。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 22, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 23, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "耶和華的使者說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 23, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "應當咒詛米羅斯，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 23, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "大大咒詛其中的居民；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 23, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "因為他們不來幫助耶和華，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 23, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "不來幫助耶和華攻擊勇士。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 23, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 24, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "願基尼人希百的妻雅億比眾婦人多得福氣，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 24, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "比住帳棚的婦人更蒙福祉。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 24, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 25, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 西西拉求水，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 25, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " 雅億給他奶子，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 25, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "用寶貴的盤子給他奶油。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 25, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 26, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 雅億左手拿着帳棚的橛子，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 26, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "右手拿着匠人的錘子，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 26, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "擊打西西拉，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 26, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "打傷他的頭，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 26, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "把他的鬢角打破穿通。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 26, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 27, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 西西拉在她腳前曲身仆倒，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 27, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "在她腳前曲身倒臥；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 27, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "在那裏曲身，就在那裏死亡。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 27, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 28, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 西西拉的母親從窗戶裏往外觀看，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 28, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "從窗櫺中呼叫說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 28, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他的戰車為何躭延不來呢？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 28, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他的車輪為何行得慢呢？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 28, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 29, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "聰明的宮女安慰她，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 29, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "她也自言自語地說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 29, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 30, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "他們莫非得財而分？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 30, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "每人得了一兩個女子？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 30, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " 西西拉得了彩衣為擄物，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 30, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "得繡花的彩衣為掠物。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 30, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "這彩衣兩面繡花，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 30, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "乃是披在被擄之人頸項上的。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 30, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 31, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "耶和華啊，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 31, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "願你的仇敵都這樣滅亡！"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 31, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "願愛你的人如日頭出現，光輝烈烈！"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 31, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "這樣，國中太平四十年。"}]}]}